description:
Description :
        Iburo, a popular GV actor, rarely gets upset because of people who interfere with his filming. He wish the director would quickly stop the filming, but instead, the director keeps shouting "cut!" which makes him even more frustrated. Can he finish filming quickly today and go home safely? Just for today, Iburo's ups and downs in GV filming as he wants to avoid working overtime!
